# Augmented Wellness — companion repo .gitignore
#
# This repo ships starter kits, prompts, source maps, claim notes, and
# agent-readable companion files. It must NOT carry secrets, cookies, raw
# media, social exports, runtime logs, or private vault data.
#
# IMPORTANT: this repo intentionally COMMITS blank seed templates and examples
# (e.g. runtime-vault-seed/, *.example.json, the example .jsonl log). The rules
# below are written to exclude live/private data while keeping those seeds.

# --- OS / editor noise ---
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
*~
.idea/
.vscode/

# --- Secrets & env ---
.env
.env.*
!.env.example
*.pem
*.key
*token*
*secret*
*credential*

# --- Cookies / sessions / browser captures ---
*cookie*
*.cookies
session.json
sessions/
*.har

# --- Social platform exports (e.g. X / Twitter archives) ---
x-export/
twitter-export/
*-twitter-archive*
*-x-archive*
tweets.js

# --- Logs (ignore live runtime logs, KEEP committed examples) ---
*.log
logs/
*.jsonl
!*.example.jsonl
!**/*.example.jsonl

# --- Local databases ---
*.db
*.sqlite
*.sqlite3

# --- Browser profiles ---
.openclaw/
chrome-profile/
browser-profile/
profiles/

# --- Generated artifacts / build output ---
dist/
build/
*.zip
codex-handoffs/

# --- Private vault runtime dirs (KEEP the blank runtime-vault-seed/) ---
# A live agent run materializes its own private vault. Never commit it.
runtime-vault/
.runtime-vault/
vault-runtime/
# (runtime-vault-seed/ is the committed BLANK seed — do not ignore it)

# --- Raw media (audio/video is hosted off-repo) ---
raw/
raw-media/
*.mp4
*.mov
*.wav
*.mp3
*.m4a

# --- Python / Node runtime ---
__pycache__/
*.pyc
node_modules/
